s/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗點解咁多人大個左冇洗過牙唔多唔少係同小學依d慘痛經驗有關</blockquote><br />\n依樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾牙科保健班撚樣SM完，以為睇牙醫就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdaf95c74eb855d08475539e773a21af20863169","tid":222521,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬時俾Ｄ姐姐玩過<br />\n補牙唔打麻醉針</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲講風涼話男孩子少少痛都忍唔到</blockquote><br />\n佢地懶得制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過大個咗 又真係唔洗打麻醉針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5e6ca4c7ab216595966384b74b408063ced05a","tid":222521,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"大過應該會後悔 有免費野唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2434391e2e712abc22734c02262e3f04f93dea1e","tid":222521,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"去完政府果d真係會有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26cc1c222e476d8a252cefd01d2a84bfa23a8d6","tid":222521,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大過應該會後悔 有免費野唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去出邊補牙先比個牙醫笑以前個位係咪大陸補<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7167b6292c8cef7d5b252af737a979bae6fd36bb","tid":222521,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年...<br />\n擘到個口最大都仲叫你擘大D<br />\n然後佢整到我甩咗骹</blockquote><br />\ntrue?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb3405a5aad72fad2aa52a6cea6bf5d44f7df64","tid":222521,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年...<br />\n擘到個口最大都仲叫你擘大D<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">然後佢整到我甩咗骹</span></blockquote><br />\n係真唔係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打乜9英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb27b042fbeacbdc4c8fa73fb4e3e99d5db68fe6","tid":222521,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大過應該會後悔 有免費野唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去出邊補牙先比個牙醫笑以前個位係咪大陸補<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前細個係用銀色料補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好核突"},{"pid":"2820f87cc5e2e77ecbb145ba51b7c293d867c21c","tid":222521,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大過應該會後悔 有免費野唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去出邊補牙先比個牙醫笑以前個位係咪大陸補<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地Ｄ牙補到牙邊好薄，到中年好易裂過隻牙就冇，好彩朋友試過，我自己去睇牙醫照Ｘ光後發現都好薄，之後做了牙套保住隻牙"},{"pid":"5078ee02f46be59bff35df9e20e3468f8b9e1c07","tid":222521,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"小一果陣蛀過六隻大牙<br />\n去完果度補完之後從此冇蛀過牙<br />\n因為唔敢食咁多甜野"},{"pid":"537643d29cb885fe812ba0fd559d4be88a058c1a","tid":222521,"uid":19363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"大個就後悔"},{"pid":"dad0c68d68df7d2384ca622aaedcba6de0658e61","tid":222521,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年...<br />\n擘到個口最大都仲叫你擘大D<br />\n然後佢整到我<span style=\"color: red;\">甩咗骹</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個口天生細，做咩要迫我喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a941c9cdc49001a55cd42078e13e3aa91c05831","tid":222521,"uid":66781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"學生唔去不如俾我地去，好過蹝左個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6572e5748c2f3823a874701addf7fb6b16b67a79","tid":222521,"uid":93394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:33:20.000Z","msg":"細個有次生爆牙 咁比佢睇完話要拔<br />\n拔完個啊嬋話要教我地刷牙<br />\n我話我啱啱拔完牙流緊血 唔刷得唔得<br />\n佢話唔洗驚叫我大力啲刷<br />\n之後吐左勁多血 個頭勁暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"4af76e8cb8fa0ae0f7e343bf9c00d74d618ccf60","tid":222521,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個有次生爆牙 咁比佢睇完話要拔<br />\n拔完個啊嬋話要教我地刷牙<br />\n我話我啱啱拔完牙流緊血 唔刷得唔得<br />\n佢話唔洗驚叫我大力啲刷<br />\n之後吐左勁多血 個頭勁暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e26fb9acf3e96248cda415ee0ca044954fa915c","tid":222521,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大過應該會後悔 有免費野唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己刷牙刷好d咪得"},{"pid":"dad183d4a6c64c9d0dbf589f3867089f2aae70f9","tid":222521,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大過應該會後悔 有免費野唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己刷牙刷好d咪得</blockquote><br />\n免費但係垃圾<br />\n我俾幾百蚊 出去 分分鐘皇帝享受<br />\n水準又高過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5bd21354a1340b9f51878b25dd8a08c7ce97d8","tid":222521,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"出面洗牙唔痛<br />\n呢個乜柒保健痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有年保健日子撞啱學校放假 畀老母夾我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啱有隻牙鬆畀個洗牙呀嬸整甩咗<br />\n個呀嬸畀我老母屌到反晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9a94642778a0486d80cadb4b15eac8cf7ff52a","tid":222521,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"童年陰影"},{"pid":"fdaea88eea156389fd2a7abcd20016621ebc8090","tid":222521,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"對上一次睇牙已經係小學<br />\n臨畢業個陣我心諗終於甩難<br />\n而家就黎廿中都唔係幾敢去睇牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bae0b3f2da1a81255a6ab5e354b26abedcd92c0","tid":222521,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"細個蛀牙俾啲人係咁講，<br />\n<br />\n之後攪到唔敢去。<br />\n<br />\n而家種左隻牙，成幾萬。屌"},{"pid":"77481c04d3e5b20f9dded616d682cb9ea461177e","tid":222521,"uid":7432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"牙科保健係小學雞嘅地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}